    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! It\u2019s the perfect fit if you\u2019re looking for something reliable and comfy without that brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
