    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain delivers linear torque and remains thermally stable under load. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox with precise linkage and positive clutch engagement. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson/Multi-link geometry performs as intended. The factory limited-slip differential provides optimal traction through the apex, while the VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. A robust, driver-spec machine with sorted internals.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
