    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained driver\u2019s car, offering a perfect blend of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with the body panels remaining straight and free of major dents. While there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use, the overall aesthetic remains sharp and professional. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the leather upholstery is clean and supple with no tears, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the heated seats, navigation system, and premium audio\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented service history that includes recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires with ample tread. It starts effortlessly, shifts smoothly, and provides a quiet, composed ride. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect and diligence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
