      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, offering a seamless balance of performance and long-term reliability. A premier choice for the driver seeking a high-caliber experience and a well-preserved interior. We invite you to experience the refined handling and dependable quality of this exceptional professional-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 36800.0,
