      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve kept up with the basics, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable car that still looks great in the driveway, this is the one! Let me know if you want to take it for a spin! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
