    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 inline-six, utilizing its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The Getrag 420G 6-speed transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The double-VANOS system is quiet and responsive, and the rear subframe\u2014a known platform vulnerability\u2014has been structurally reinforced for long-term durability. It rides on a well-sorted suspension with refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the chassis remains neutral and communicative through the corners. While showing minor signs of road use, the mechanical integrity of the drivetrain and the rigidity of the subframe make this a driver-focused example ready for the track or the street.",
